des:
Amen FM, the first Tamil Christian Radio Station found by Sis. Carmen Lawrence and Bro. Lawrence Joseph on February 14, 2004. Amen FM offers you a fresh blend of Praise and Worship music. The songs are carefully selected, vertically focused, and designed to lift your Spirit every time you listen. 

The content of this Skill is in Tamil.
